Subject: 6/2 DC Action . . .
Date: 31 May 1996 07:37:50 -0800 (PST)

From:  tom@igc.apc.org 
Received: (from tom) by igc2.igc.apc.org (8.7.5/8.7.3) id HAA24503; Fri, 31 May 1996 07:27:50 -0700 (PDT)
Date: Fri, 31 May 1996 07:27:50 -0700 (PDT)

From prop1@prop1.org  Thu May 30 23:19:52 1996
Return-Path: prop1@prop1.org
Received: from pooky.myhouse.com (pooky.myhouse.com [204.156.22.2]) by igc7.igc.apc.org (8.7.5/8.7.3) with ESMTP id XAA26339; Thu, 30 May 1996 23:19:51 -0700 (PDT)
Received: from prop1.laurel.us.net (prop1.laurel.us.net [198.240.66.227]) by pooky.myhouse.com (8.7.4/8.7.3) with SMTP id CAA27384; Fri, 31 May 1996 02:24:09 -0400 (EDT)
Date: Fri, 31 May 1996 02:24:09 -0400 (EDT)
Message-Id:  199605310624.CAA27384@pooky.myhouse.com 
