This registration form may be sent by mail or fax to the attention
of Ms. Ginger Mann, Duke University School of Law, Box 90389, Durham,
North Carolina, USA 27708-0389.  Fax # (919) 613-7231.

NOTE:  Registration by e-mail will tentatively reserve your place.
In addition to responding by e-mail, please forward the completed and
signed registration by fax or mail <a name=L10001></a><a href=#L10002>so</a> that your payment can be
processed and your registration confirmed.  Thank you.

For  additional information, contact Professor Madeline Morris or
Ms. Ginger Mann at Duke University School of Law, Durham, North
Carolina, USA.

Professor Madeline Morris
 Telephone:                      (919) 613-7049
