From: "David Yarrow"  dyarrow@igc.apc.org 

   Friday, April 26 I received this letter:

Earth Day, April 22, 1996

Dear David,

   I was astonished when a sister in my Meditation Circle handed me your 
flyer on World Peace and Prayer Day, as I've been carrying the Great 
Pyramid Prophecy for Summer Solstice 1996 to people on the humble scale 
of my own publishing efforts.  See enclosed flyer and 4-page prophecy.

   I'd be grateful if you pass on copies of these to Arvol Looking Horse 
and those organizing activities around his mission.  I enclose cash for 
costs of copies and postage.

   I look forward to join in Solstice prayers from the mystic tradition 
of the Temple of the Great Initiation -- of which I've been initiate 
and teacher for over two decades -- with all people of all traditions -- 
especially our native brothers and sisters -- for healing of the Earth 
and transformation of consciousness in Unity and Universal Love.

   I'm very interested in further information about events unfolding 
around the tradition of the White Buffalo Calf mystery, and the meaning 
and how the prophecy and Star Knowledge are manifesting.

   Blessings upon your work, Mikiel

   *************************************************************

                 The Great Pyramid Prophecy
                              for
                     Summer Solstice 1996

   Let it be known to all, as given by the Great Pyramid, that 
we, as a global family, are "at the door of the House of God" 
as this summer approaches.  (God and Goddess are One.)

   Many prophecies confirm 1996 as a Year of Awakening from the sleep 
of ego -- the illusion of separateness as individuals and groups -- into 
One Consciousness in all -- Source of Universal Love.  Let peoples of 
all traditions join in prayer for planetary healing and peace at the 
Solstice "high Light" of this year.

   On the door of the Pyramid's inner sanctum (called "Secret House 
of God" in Egyptian scripture) is a rainbow-shaped sign displaying the 
"sacred cubit" -- divine standard of measure -- which we pass 
beneath (on the prophetic time-distance scale) this Solstice in 
preparation to begin passing through the Door by the end of July.  The 
Door spans to 2014 when the transition into the new Millennium (and the 
dimension of awareness of omnipresent divinity) will be complete.

                 for more information, write to:
             Mikiel, P. O. Box 103, Eugene, OR  97440
                    (please enclose SASE)

        Spirit Speaks to the Inner Ear Where Truth is Known

