Subject: judge gives nuxalk suspended senten
Date: 28 Jun 1996 09:29:57

Subject: judge gives nuxalk suspended sentences


---------- Forwarded message ----------
Date: Thu, 27 Jun 1996 18:54:37 -0700
From: greg higgs  fan@alternatives.com 
Subject: FAN press release

