Subject: Elorriaga and Entzin Freed!
Date: 06 Jun 1996 21:16:46



-------------- Enclosure number 1 ----------------
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
         National Commission for Democracy in Mexico
               601 N. Cotton St., Suite #A103
                      El Paso, TX 79902
                     ph/fx (915)532-8382
                email: moonlight@igc.apc.org
                              
                              
