<DOCOLDNO>IA021-000226-B032-434</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.knooppunt.be:80/~hit_run/caerts/akai_s.html 194.10.201.200 19970107175739 text/html 12650
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
