<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Cybersound VS</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BACKGROUNDCOLOR="ffffff" TEXT="#000000"  background="http://www.knooppunt.be/~hit_run/caerts/logoback.gif">
<img align=right src="http://www.knooppunt.be/~hit_run/caerts/cybersnd.gif">
<img align=top src="http://www.knooppunt.be/~hit_run/caerts/cybersnd.jpg">
<h2>The Software Synthesizer
for Your Macintosh</h2><hr>

<h3>Over 500 Sounds. Digital Effects. Built-in MIDI Sequencing. Incredibly Affordable.</h3>

<h5>CyberSound VS is an entirely new way to make music with your Mac. With just a simple-to-install CD-ROM, you can turn any PowerPC Macintosh
into a full-fledged MIDI synthesizer -- with no additional hardware needed! You can even use it with many PowerBooks: Just add headphones, and
you're ready to work on your tunes anywhere.</h5><hr>

<b>CyberSound VS gives you
more than most synthesizers --
and comes complete on a CD-ROM!</b><p>

If you're looking for a versatile MIDI synthesizer, CyberSound VS
delivers the goods -- with hundreds of sounds (and many more in
development). If you've ever envied PC users, with their choice of
dozens of synth-equipped sound cards, you'll love what
CyberSound VS can do for your Mac. CyberSound VS not only
works like a MIDI sound card, but goes far beyond the synth
capabilities of any card available, for any computer platform.<p>

<b>No matter how you work with
sound or music, you'll love what
CyberSound VS lets you do:</b>
<ul>
<li>Playing: Get 512 fantastic sounds, digital effects, upgradable sound
libraries, and more! 
<li>Recording & Editing: CyberSound VS includes CyberPlayer, a
MIDI recorder/player that's fast and easy to use, on your desktop, in the studio, or
even on the road. 
<li>Composing: Pros will love CyberSound VS's compositional
features -- but even a novice can get into the groove with a variety of one-finger
rhythm, dance, techno and rap loops. 
<li>Multimedia Producing: With General MIDI
(GM), QuickTime and lots more, CyberSound VS brings new sonic power to
anyone developing games, reference works, or even multimedia presentations!
</ul>
<hr>
<h2>FEATURES</h2>
<ul>
<li>A complete Synth-on-a-Disk for all PowerPC & 68040 Macs 
<li>PowerPC-native performance
<li>No extra hardware needed
<li>Up to l28-note polyphony (dependent upon CPU)
<li>512 Sound Programs, contained within 9 Bank Files
<li>9 Drum Sets include 165 drum & percussion sounds
<li>50 megabytes of InVision Interactive 16-bit samples
<li>General MIDI (GM), General Standard (GS), & future QuickTime compatibility
<li>Sounds created using multiple sound technologies, including wavetable, analog & digital synthesis models, & hysical modeling
<li>Programmable reverb & chorus digital effects with individual parameter controls
<li>Includes Cyberplayer, a 16-track MIDI recorder/player
<li>Sounds selectable from the CyberSound VS Control Panel, MIDI, or via CyberPlayer
<li>Full 16-channel multitimbral support
<li>Trigger sounds from a mouse or QWERTY keyboard (no MIDI controller required)
<li>Supports MIDI Manage OMS, & freeMIDI for use with 3rd party sequencers
<li>Dynamically loadable wavetable library
<li>User-configurable variable RAM cache
<li>Save & reload custom setups in a flash
<li>Wavetable oversampling for highest possible fidelity
<li>Intelligent Scaling adjusts CyberSound VS to available CPU power
<li>Diagnostics window (included) monitors system performance
<li>MIDI activity indicators on all 16 MIDI channels
<li>On-Screen Balloon Help
<li>Automated Installer for easy set-up
</ul>
<hr>
<h2>The First Pro-Quality Synth-On-A-Disk for the Macintosh</h2>
<b>CyberSound VS turns your Mac into a pro synth with
hundreds of great sounds. No additional hardware needed!</b><br>

<ul>
<li>CyberSound VS comes complete, installs in minutes on most Macs -- including many PowerBooks -- and is amazingly easy to use.
<li>Everything you need is included on one simple-to-install CD-ROM disc.
<li>Includes programmable digital reverb and chorus effects (PowerPC only). Gives your music pro-quality audio DSP effects with just a few mouse clicks.
<li>Supports General MIDI (GM), General Standard (GS) and QuickTime -- so CyberSound VS is what you need if you're scoring music for multimedia. Or want to be.
</ul>

<b>Think of it as a killer sample & rhythm loop CD --
with a free synth</b>

<ul>
<li>CyberSound VS gives you 512 impressive sounds. You'll hear full-bodied pianos; luscious orchestral instruments; realistic guitars and basses; powerful drum kits; wild ethnic instruments; outrageous dance, techno and rap loops; synth tones; plus a lot more.
<li>Get 50 megabytes of acclaimed 16-bit sounds from InVision Interactive. Ordinary synths have just four to 12 megabytes, so CyberSound VS may give you more sonic diversity than the rest of your studio combined.
<li>CyberSound VS is crafted using the best sound creation technologies available, including wavetable sounds, analog and digital synth models, and even physical modeling.
<li>With its dance, techno and rap loops, touch a single key (or click your mouse) and CyberSound VS will have you making music with just one finger!
</ul>


<b>CyberSound VS makes a great first (or second, or third) synth -- for a great price</b>

<ul>
<li>No matter how sophisticated or simple your studio may be, CyberSound VS's 512 unique sounds are a perfect sonic complement to any studio.
<li>Get up to 128 simultaneous voices with a PowerMac 9500.
<li>With many megabytes' worth of future sound libraries already in development, CyberSound VS will be ready to grow when you are.
</ul>


<b>PowerBook portability -- the heart of a traveling studio</b>

<ul>
<li>Fits in your pocket -- and runs on many PowerBooks. Make music wherever you are, whenever.
<li>Don't have a MIDI keyboard handy? No problem: Use your computer's keyboard to work on your tunes.
</ul>

<b>Includes CyberPlayer, a 16-track MIDI recorder/player</b>

<ul>
<li>CyberPlayer is a quick, easy-to-use 16-track MIDI sequencer with loads of features.
<li>CyberPlayer also records from any MIDI controller for playback with CyberSound VS.
<li>OMS, FreeMIDI, and MIDI Manager-compatible for use with many professional Mac sequencers.
</ul>


<b>No MIDI or music experience required</b>

<ul>
<li>On-screen Balloon Help whenever, and wherever you need it!
</ul>

