<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>

<H2>A Proud Tradition, A Progressive Future</H2></CENTER>

<P>McMillan Binch is one of Canada's leading full service business 
law firms, serving domestic and international enterprises, 
financial institutions, governments and private individuals 
wherever there is a need for definitive legal advice on complex 
matters.</P>

<P>We pride ourselves on adding value to our clients' businesses 
by providing the best possible proactive legal advice based on 
our extensive cross-Canada and cross-border experience and our 
ongoing awareness of developments in the law and in the 
marketplace.</P>

<P>Our approach is focused on the need to meet client objectives 
in a timely and cost-effective manner.  We adhere to the 
highest professional standards while still maintaining 
effective working relationships with all parties to a 
transaction. More information about our <A HREF="BusArr.html">Business Arrangements </A> and <A HREF="Disburse.html">Disbursement Policy</A>
can be found in the attached text.</P>

<P>Founded in 1903, we have approximately 138 lawyers with a total 
staff of 400 working in our <A HREF="Toronto.html">Toronto Office</A>.</P>

<P>McMillan Binch is a member of <A HREF="MBulCas.html">McMillan Bull Casgrain</A>, a national association and international partnership.</P>

<DL><DD><IMG SRC="AboutP.gif">

<DL><DD>For more information about a specific
area of our practice,<BR>
please click on your choice:</DL></DL>
