<H1>Disbursement Policy</H1>
<DL><DD>
<P>Any out-of-pocket expenses we incur on your behalf are charged to you at our cost.<BR>Our
typical disbursements and charges are:</P>
<DD><TABLE CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0>
<TR><TD><B>Disbursement</B></TD><TD><B>Charge</B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD>External database on-line charges . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Telecommunication (voice, data, fax) charges. . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Photocopies . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>10 per page  </TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Court filing, discovery and transcript fees . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Filing and search fees. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Prior approved overtime for secretarial, . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Overtime premium</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>word processing or non-legal staff</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Agents and consultants retained by us . . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Registered mail/special delivery . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Courier or cab deliveries. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Our messenger . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>$2-8 per delivery,</TD></TR>
<TR><TD></TD><TD><I>(depending on urgency)</I></TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Other prior approved out-of-pocket expenses . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Travel and expenses. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</TD><TD>Actual cost</TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN=2><I>(Ordinarily, flights less than 3 hours are economy class and longer flights are<BR>
business class. We exercise reasonable judgment and restraint for accommodation,<BR>
food and incidental expenses.)</I></TD></TR></TABLE>
<BR><BR><BR>
