<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>

<H1>Banking, Structured Finance and Derivatives</H1>

<P>Our financial services lawyers have a worldwide reputation and act for Canadian and
international financial institutions and borrowers on all types of financing transactions
both in Canada and internationally.  Their expertise covers domestic and international
financing, syndicated loans, sovereign credit, securitizations, infrastructure and project
financing, balance sheet enhancement techniques, risk reduction techniques, domestic and
cross-border leasing, structured instruments and over-the counter and exchange-traded
derivative products including interest rate and currency swaps, equity derivative products
and commodity based derivative products.  They also provide ongoing advice to all types of
Canadian and international financial institutions on compliance with federal and
provincial regulatory regimes.</P>
