<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>

<H1>Securities/Corporate Finance</H1>

<P>Our securities lawyers act for a variety of clients (including domestic and foreign
issuers of debt and equity securities, municipal and provincial governments, financial
institutions, investment banks and securities dealers) and have extensive experience in
all areas of securities law.  Their practice covers a wide range of capital markets
transactions, including public equity and debt offerings (both domestic and cross-border),
government finance, private placements and the development and implementation of mutual
and pooled funds.  In addition, their expertise extends to dealing with the regulatory
compliance matters and securities litigation in the courts and before administrative
tribunals and to providing advice to governments on securities regulation policy.</P>
<IMG SRC="ScaleP.gif">
<CENTER><TABLE>
