<H1>Corporate and Commercial</H1>

<P>Our corporate and commercial lawyers carry on a comprehensive and fully integrated
business law practice.  They advise on and assist in the formation and organization of
businesses including large corporate reorganizations, mergers, acquisitions, divestitures,
takeovers, management buyouts, international business arrangements, foreign investment,
joint ventures, licensing and technology transfers.</P>
