<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>

<H1>Competition and International Trade</H1>

<P>Our international trade lawyers provide strategic planning assistance to clients seeking
to capitalize on the emergence of the world's trading zones.  They advise on trade
treaties like NAFTA and the World Trade Organization Agreement and the impact those
treaties have on business.  Our competition and antitrust lawyers provide advice and
assistance on all aspects of Canadian competition law and policy, including mergers,
collaboration between competitors, pricing, marketing and distribution practices,
compliance program audits, investigations and litigation.  The group is an acknowledged
leader in its field and has been involved in a number of high profile Canadian and
international mergers.</P>
