<H1>Corporate Restructuring and Insolvency</H1>

<P>Our corporate restructuring and insolvency lawyers advise creditors, corporations,
directors, insolvency accountants and others on all matters relating to corporate
restructuring, receiverships, bankruptcies, liquidations and distressed debt trading. 
They provide innovative and effective solutions to insolvency problems and to the
management of insolvency risks when structuring new transactions.  Their expertise extends
to public and private, domestic and international corporate insolvencies and includes
extensive experience in particular with Canadian/US cross-border issues.</P>
