<H1>Commodity Tax</H1>

<P>Our commodity tax lawyers provide advice on customs valuation and tariff classification,
value-added taxes, GST, retail sales taxes, anti-dumping and countervailing duties and
import/export permits, licenses and quotas.  Their expertise includes the representation
of importers and exporters in resolving issues with customs and trade administration
authorities and regular appearances before appeal tribunals.</P>
