<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>

<H1>Insurance</H1>

<P>Our insurance lawyers advise on all aspects of insurance law including corporate,
regulatory and litigation requirements applicable to life and property and casualty
companies.  Their expertise also extends to providing advice on overall insurance programs
for our clients, sometimes in conjunction with other professionals such as insurance
brokers and consultants.</P>
