<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>

<H1>KNOW<I>law</I></H1>

<P>The KNOW<I>law</I><FONT SIZE="-1"></FONT> group provides advice in the areas of communications, entertainment and media
law and intellectual property rights and technology law.  Working primarily with companies
in the knowledge-based industries, their expertise extends to the acquisition, development
and protection of ownership of intangible assets, forming joint ventures for the
development or modernization of technology, structuring and negotiating financing for
product development and compliance with consumer protection and other government
regulations.  They provide advice on the distribution, licensing, franchising and
advertising of products, on transfers of technology and on matters of proprietary
ownership of intangible property including the protection of trademarks, copyrights,
patents, industrial designs and other confidential information.</P>

