<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>

<H1>Labour/Employment/Immigration/Pensions</H1>

<P>Our labour/employment lawyers provide advice on all aspects of labour and employment law
representing clients before government labour relations and pension boards, arbitrators,
adjudicators, referees and human rights boards of inquiry as well as in workers'
compensation, pay and employment equity and occupational health and safety proceedings.
Their expertise extends to advising corporate clients on the establishment, administration
and winding up of pension plans, dismissals and severance arrangements, senior executives'
employment contracts, and the employment and pension aspects of acquisitions, divestitures
and corporate reorganizations.  They also provide advice on a broad range of immigration
matters, including foreign employee recruitment.</P>
