<H1>Litigation</H1>

<P>Our litigation lawyers offer extensive professional experience and expertise in matters of
civil litigation including banking, corporate, securities, competition, mergers and
acquisitions, commercial fraud, environment, insurance and reinsurance, product liability,
public/private sector disputes, aviation, estates, professional liability, admiralty,
employment, insolvency, constitutional and real estate litigation.  They appear regularly
before all levels of federal and provincial courts and administrative boards and
tribunals.  They also engage in private arbitration and alternative dispute resolution
proceedings in order to offer a full range of dispute resolution services to our
clients.</P>
