<H1>Private Client and Family Services</H1>

<P>Our private client and family lawyers address individual, estate, family and taxation
planning needs including advising on confidential relationships and privacy issues,
domestic and international personal tax planning, marriage contracts, cohabitation
agreements and separation agreements, estate administration, immigration and emigration,
the expansion and succession of family businesses, the disposition of family real estate,
the establishment and variation of inter-vivos trusts and a variety of matter related to
charitable giving.</P>
