<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>
<H1>Real Property Development and the Environment</H1>

<P>Our real property lawyers advise major developers, financial institutions and
international private investors in all aspects of commercial and residential real estate
development and financing as well as related restructuring.  Their expertise also extends
to land use planning, assessment, expropriation and municipal law, with particular
emphasis on appearances before municipal councils and land use tribunals.  Our
environmental lawyers work closely with real property lawyers and project lenders,
advising on environmental assessments, due diligence and environmental audits and lender
liability issues.</P>
