<IMG SRC="AboutH.gif"><BR>
<H1>Taxation</H1>

<P>Tax efficiency is a significant component of virtually every transaction from the simplest
to the most complex.  Our tax lawyers, always sensitive to business goals, provide advice
on corporate reorganizations, mergers and acquisitions, securities, structured financing
and derivative products, leasing and international cross-border transactions.  They
routinely advise clients on compliance matters and are experienced in negotiating disputes
with revenue authorities and litigating on tax issues.</P>
<IMG SRC="ScaleP.gif">
