 <P><H2>Protection of Intellectual Property</H2>
</P>
<P>
<H3><I>"John Perry Barlow set the stage in <A HREF="http://www.hotwired.com">Wired</A>"</I></H3>
<FONT SIZE=+1><P><UL><LI><A HREF="eco1-xfr.htm" > THE ECONOMY OF IDEAS Part 1</A> by John Perry Barlow<LI><A HREF="eco2-xfr.htm" > THE ECONOMY OF IDEAS Part 2</A> by John Perry Barlow<LI><A HREF="eco3-xfr.htm" > THE ECONOMY OF IDEAS Part 3</A> by John Perry Barlow<LI><A HREF="eco4-xfr.htm" > THE ECONOMY OF IDEAS Part 4</A> by John Perry Barlow</UL></P>
<P></P>
<P></P> 
<P>
