 <P><H2>Where Is Here?</H2>
</P>
<FONT SIZE=+1><P><UL><LI><A HREF="http://roscoe.law.harvard.edu/courses/techseminar96/course/sessions/jurisdiction/jurisdiction.html" > Internet Technology & Personal Jurisdiction, by Colin Stretch. </A><LI><A HREF="http://www.ssbb.com/whatjuri.html" > What Jurisdiction Controls?, by Satterlee Stephens Burke & Burke. </UL></A></P>
<P></P>
