</P>
<FONT SIZE=+1><P><UL><LI><A HREF="http://diamond.mtk.nao.ac.jp/~bfr/McSpotkit/tok/media/press/mcsp_heats.html" > "McLibel Case Heats Up On Internet" by Beth Karlin</A><LI><A HREF="http://diamond.mtk.nao.ac.jp/~bfr/McSpotkit/tok/media/press/mcsp_bloomberg.html" > "McDonalds Critics Take Case To Net As Trial Drags On" by Beth Karlin</UL></A></P>
