</P>
<FONT SIZE=+1><P><UL><LI><A HREF="tsld017.htm" > Shae v. Reno; ACLU v. Reno</A><LI><A HREF="http://www.newshare.com:9999/decision.html" > Text of decision in Shea v. Reno</A><LI><A HREF="http://www.aclu.org/court/cdadec.html" > Text of decision in ACLU v. Reno</A><LI><A HREF="http://www.epic.org/free_speech/censorship/cda.txt" > Full text of CDA</A><LI><A HREF="http://www.hotwired.com/architext/AT-HotWiredquery.html" > Links to a number of Netizen documents re: internet censorship</A><LI> <A HREF="http://pegasus.cc.ucf.edu/~mab17431/ip.htm" > Censorship on the Internet by Marty Bruce</A><LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/headlines/special/cda/cda.1.html" > Reuters: Decision in Internet Suit Due Wednesday</A><LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/headlines/special/cda/cda.2.html" > Reuters: US Court Strikes Down Internet Indecency Law</A><LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/headlines/special/cda/cda.3.html" > Reuters: Victory for Free Speech on Internet</A><LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/headlines/special/cda/cda.4.html" > Reuters: U.S. Court Blocks New Internet-Indecency Law</UL></A></P>
